    <div class="card">
      <h1>09 — Purpose, Calling & Service</h1>
      <p><b>Goal:</b> To discover purpose and express calling through service and impact.</p>

      <h2>Key Scriptures</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><b>Ephesians 2:10</b> — Created for good works prepared by God.</li>
        <li><b>Jeremiah 1:5</b> — Ordained before birth.</li>
        <li><b>Romans 12:6–8</b> — Different gifts, same grace.</li>
        <li><b>Matthew 20:26–28</b> — Greatness in the Kingdom is service.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Truths to Note</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Calling is discovered in God’s presence and confirmed by fruit.</li>
        <li>Purpose grows as you serve faithfully where you are planted.</li>
        <li>Spiritual gifts are for building others, not self-promotion.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Action Steps</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Write 3 burdens God has placed on your heart.</li>
        <li>Pick one area of service in church/community and commit.</li>
        <li>Ask a mentor for guidance and accountability.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Prayer Points</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Father, unveil my purpose and align me with Your will.</li>
        <li>Let my life be useful in Your hands, in Jesus’ Name.</li>
        <li>I receive grace for faithful service and lasting impact.</li>
      </ul>

